Since blockchain records are immutable, fake or duplicate documents cannot be created.
Any attempt to alter data is automatically rejected by the system.
âœ” Reduces land scams and disputes.
4ï¸. Smart Contracts for Property Transactions
Tamil Nadu plans to use smart contracts for:
Sale agreements
